{"tid":2285831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"過咗咁耐，你哋仲驚唔驚中武漢肺炎？","createTime":"2020-11-14T12:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T18:41:34.000Z","uid":25084,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4519400686c8fb58146926b4b6abf196e52493","tid":2285831,"uid":25084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"日日返工放工時間地鐵巴士都迫爆，隔離有個確診都好大機會中，咁近距離又唔係戴N95加著保護衣。<br />\n遲下仲每日放5000個粵港免檢人士落嚟通街走，今次仲唔係大爆發，強制檢測好時機？！<br />\n<br />\n搞咩限聚令、社交距離。到底係政府廢定係根本利用人嘅恐惧做政治打壓，限制自由？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚驚，同流感差唔多，驚西咩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚，我同屋企人都好怕死。"},{"pid":"8f3d9c8f8db803c95046d59e0d7d90d79710d9b3","tid":2285831,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"其實唔係幾驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512a83a7aa08c3f6e43405a87dfb42aef644f0ba","tid":2285831,"uid":37487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"1日1千個都要返工架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a025e04890c2db8be0e07ea2f4fae18b2b468dfe","tid":2285831,"uid":314177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512a83a7aa08c3f6e43405a87dfb42aef644f0ba","tid":2285831,"uid":37487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"1日1千個都要返工架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/do